This repository is for the training bots

command to build docker image:
```
docker build --platform=linux/arm64/v8 -t image_name:tag .
```

docker save -o training-bot.tar training-bot-base:pi-1.0

scp training-bot.tar mars@larry.local:~/Downloads


ON PI
docker load -i ~/Downloads/training-bot.tar

to run
docker run -it --rm --device=/dev/input/event4 --device=/dev/ttyACM0 training-bot-base:pi-1.0